description.en:
SIPHER is the multifunctional governance token of the Sipher Universe. The token is used as a payment currency to clone new characters, staking, and ecosystem incentives for developers and contributors.

The Sipher Universe is a blockchain based game focused on casual fighting and exploration with the goal of creating an open world social experience for players.
